{
  "stem": "311.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, she went-- she-- she was working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't know where to stop, once they taught her how to do it, you know, on the sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The last thing I heard, when they took out, from Plaszow, she went to Stutthof, which wasn't such a bad concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And something happened that-- they-- they wanted to save-- who-- I don't know if it was a German or a working camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to save, from Stutthof, some people and bring them to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was something like Schindler, whatever, you know, somebody?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a bombing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they start yelling, those women and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The ones that kept quiet, some of them made it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the ones that they start yelling, the people had to choke them, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whatever, this-- and that's where she-- that-- this was the end of my Aunt Berta.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Berta?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother and my sister, all those people went, I think, to Treblinka at that time, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after the war, you know, Rav Lewertow was a friend of he was a-- the-- the baker rabbi of Cracow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is dynasty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is no-- once they have it, this is father to son and to grand-- you know, that's how it goes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Cracow dynasty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This has completely got nothing to do with Hasidic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think this is the law.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how they're set up in the City of Cracow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] they set up it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made the first day of Rosh Chodesh Kislev, but Rosh Chodesh Kislev can be two days, certain years, right?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe around November, October time?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I just have a card.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, it's out.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
